    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "This 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S offers a visceral driving experience powered by the 3.6L M96 flat-six engine featuring VarioCam Plus timing. The drivetrain utilizes a robust Getrag G96/31 6-speed manual transaxle delivering power to an all-wheel-drive system with a viscous coupling. Chassis dynamics are sharp, featuring the factory wide-body configuration and 'Big Red' four-piston monobloc calipers with cross-drilled rotors. Extensive preventative maintenance includes a retrofitted LN Engineering IMS bearing and a fresh rear main seal. The suspension remains taut with Bilstein dampers, providing excellent lateral grip and communicative feedback through the hydraulic steering rack. A mechanically sound example of the 996.2 generation.",
      "price": 38500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
