    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle has been a reliable and cherished daily driver, meticulously maintained to ensure longevity. The exterior retains a beautiful shine, though you will find minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear passenger bumper\u2014typical for its age but hardly noticeable from a distance. Inside, the cabin is smoke-free and features supple leather upholstery with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster. Every button, switch, and digital display functions exactly as intended, including the premium sound system and dual-zone climate control. Mechanically, the car is sound; it has received synthetic oil changes every 5,000 miles, and the brakes were recently serviced with OEM parts. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining. It drives straight, shifts smoothly, and offers a quiet, composed ride. I have a full folder of service records available for your review. This is an excellent opportunity to own a well-cared-for example that balances performance with everyday practicality.",
